    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Events or processes resulting in a species or multiple species dying out and having no living representatives. Extinctions may be natural events or the result of human activity.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
